::Iron Fist::

The cargo hold's doors open, letting Angel Prime out of the ship and 
keeping the pod inside, shutting and locking. The bombs did very 
little to the ship as they exploded, leaving slight scorch marks on 
the hull.

The defences returned fire, taking some hits and continuing to fire 
missiles and laser shots at Angel Prime.
